%F A058212 From _Paul Barry_, Mar 18 2004: (Start)
%F A058212 G.f.: (1 - 2x + x^2 + x^4)/((1 - x)^2(1 - x^3)).
%F A058212 a(n) = 4*cos(2*Pi*n/3)/9 + (3*n^2 - 9*n + 10)/18. (End)
